About the SourceYou can use this source for any purposes.  We make no guarnantee that it is useful for anything.  If you do use the source, it'd be a nice gesture if you sent us a free copy of whatever program you're writing.Stairways Software Pty LtdPO Box 1123Booragoon WA 6154AUSTRALIASome of the files are old  code.  Some use CW10.  Soime require small hacks to the interfaces (Universal Interfaces, Open Transport interfaces, etc).  Some of the files in the Libraries folder are simply Pascal translations of various other API files floating around the net.Enjoy,   Peter.